Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.74,0:00:15.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走起來\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Move!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.00,0:00:17.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我天生就是打仗的料\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- I was born for battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.08,0:00:20.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,具備打仗應有的素質\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Built for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.17,0:00:26.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有時在戰斗中 精心設計的計劃會遭破壞\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Sometimes in battle, a perfectly crafted plan gets compromised.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.51,0:00:31.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一位真正的將軍 當場就能想出一個更好的計劃\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}A true general comes up with a better one right there on the spot,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.76,0:00:34.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冒著風險采取行動\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}working without a net
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.43,0:00:40.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后在雷鳴般的掌聲中 圓滿地完成任務\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and sticking the landing to thunderous applause.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.32,0:00:46.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點 狗崽子們\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Hurry up, you dogs!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.07,0:00:48.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快走\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Let's go! Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.95,0:00:56.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們在哪兒\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Where are they?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.95,0:00:59.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們當時直沖我們過來 然后轉到了一條側軌上\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- They were coming straight at us and then veered away on a sidetrack.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.96,0:01:01.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這條軌道拐向西南方\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This line bends Southwest.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.25,0:01:03.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以那個速度 他們此刻可能已在20公里之外\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}At that speed, they could be 20 kilometers away by now.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.84,0:01:05.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或者已調頭 跟在我們后面\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Or coming about to nip at our heels.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.50,0:01:07.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 先生 這事事先沒一點征兆\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- I'm sorry, sir. There was no warning.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.09,0:01:10.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然 他們確保了這一點 不是嗎  趁沒有衛星信號\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- No, they saw to that, didn't they? No satellite coverage.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.55,0:01:12.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在無月之夜 從陰影中伏擊我們\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}A moonless night. An ambush from the shadows!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.01,0:01:14.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就跟他們離開的那天一樣懦弱\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- As cowardly as the day they left, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.89,0:01:16.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 他們從我們身邊經過肯定有陰謀\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- No, they didn't drive by for nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.77,0:01:19.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把前燈開到最大\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Forward lamps to full.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.44,0:01:23.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剎車\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Brake!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.94,0:01:30.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在戰斗中 有那么一刻 你被對方的第一擊擊中后\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}There's a moment in a fight when that first blow lands
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.57,0:01:32.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一切仿佛都靜止了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and everything stops.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.99,0:01:37.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那一瞬間 你心開目明 認清了自己是誰\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And in that flash of clarity, you know who you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.91,0:01:42.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會竭盡全力奪回我的機車\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'll push as hard as it takes to get my engine back.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.17,0:01:47.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,1023節車廂長的雪國列車\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Snowpiercer, 1,023 cars long.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.94,0:02:07.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加大馬力 沖過去\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Full thrust. Push through it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.36,0:02:10.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-可是 先生 如果車軸… -全速前進 工程師 快\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Sir, if that axel-- - Full power, Engineer. Now!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.54,0:02:21.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干得漂亮 先生 第一局您贏了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Well done, sir. Round one to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.87,0:02:25.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 他們放那個陷阱 不是為了讓我們停下\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- No, no, that trap wasn't meant to stop us.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.38,0:02:26.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而是為了讓我們減速\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It was meant to slow us down.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.92,0:02:28.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凱文 我們今天不能受任何挫折\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We can't have any setbacks today, Kevin.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.84,0:02:31.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魯絲的人會受到激勵的 去把他們找出來\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Ruth's people will be energized. Find them.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.46,0:02:32.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我正好知道該從何著手\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- I know just where to start.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.92,0:02:34.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手段狠點\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Take the gloves off.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.05,0:02:36.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,殺雞儆猴\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Make an example.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.64,0:02:39.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就等著您這么吩咐呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- I thought you'd never ask.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.02,0:02:42.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-凱文 還有件事 -您說 先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- And Kevin? - Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.48,0:02:45.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓扎拉到這里來\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Send Zarah to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.86,0:02:49.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們現在的速度是多少\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What's our speed?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.44,0:02:51.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每小時14公里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- 14 kilometers an hour.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.28,0:02:54.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啊 雷頓先生 你已迫使我們慢如爬行\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- All right, Mr. Layton, you got us at a crawl.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.57,0:02:56.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有什么花招呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What's the play?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.54,0:03:02.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷頓知道車尾對接是行不通的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Layton knows better than to connect end to end.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.95,0:03:05.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我手下的軍靴可以直接沖進去擊敗他\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}My Jackboots would just sweep in and crush him.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.29,0:03:09.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 他會從側面襲擊我們\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So he's going to peck at us from the side.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.54,0:03:10.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他需要一條并行的軌道\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- He needs parallel track.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.71,0:03:13.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而這片鐵路站場就像個迷宮 布滿了并行軌道\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- And this rail yard is an entire maze of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.06,0:03:32.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們擺脫了陷阱 但速度慢了下來\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He broke free of the snare but slowed down.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.23,0:03:35.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們可以在這些側線上 趕上他們 與其并行\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- We can get right up alongside him in these sidings.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.86,0:03:38.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們距離那里還有2公里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They'll be in position in 2 kilometers.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.16,0:03:39.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本 調頭\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Bring us around, Ben.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.41,0:03:40.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-收到 -有多少時間\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Copy that. - How long we got?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.58,0:03:41.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三四分鐘\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Three, four minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.49,0:03:43.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 機警點 咱們把這事給辦了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- All right, stay sharp. Let's get this done.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.33,0:03:44.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去確保喬西已做好準備\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'll make sure Josie's ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.00,0:03:48.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貝絲\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Bess.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.13,0:03:52.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貝絲提爾\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}♪ Bess Till
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.84,0:03:55.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-貝絲  -奧德麗 閉嘴\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}♪ Bess! - Audrey, shut it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.63,0:03:58.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出什么事了 是他嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- What's happening? Is it him?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.01,0:04:01.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他的腦袋被插在長矛上時 你就會知道是他了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- You'll know it's him when his head is on a pike.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.52,0:04:10.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你準備好了嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- You ready for this?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.73,0:04:14.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本開到他們邊上后 我就跳過去 進大愛麗絲的機車\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Ben takes us close. I jump over, breach the Big Alice engine,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.57,0:04:15.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后你們重新連接兩車\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and you reconnect.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.44,0:04:17.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們只有一次機會\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- We only get one shot at it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.57,0:04:21.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就最好別錯失這個機會\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Well, then, better not miss it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.18,0:04:48.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,扎拉\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Zarah,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.14,0:04:49.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你來得正是時候\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}just in time.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.14,0:04:51.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得你該看看這個\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Thought you should be here for this.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.81,0:04:53.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以人質的身份還是旁觀者的身份\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- As a hostage or a spectator?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.69,0:04:55.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以我的紅顏知己的身份\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- As my confidante, nothing less.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.07,0:04:56.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Come.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.65,0:04:58.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.45,0:05:02.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看一下\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Have a look.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.24,0:05:05.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看到沒\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}See,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.62,0:05:08.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從我們側翼悄悄追上來的 是你的舊相好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}that's your old life creeping up our flank.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.41,0:05:10.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們要攻擊我們嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Are they attacking?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.75,0:05:13.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也許他們是來投降的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Maybe they're here to surrender.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.25,0:05:15.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看到白旗了嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You see any white flags?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.67,0:05:21.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-沒有 -沒有\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- No. - No.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.30,0:05:22.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果非得讓我猜的話\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No, and if I had to guess,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.47,0:05:25.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得他們是沖著龍首而來的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'd say they're trying to cut the head off the snake.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.01,0:05:27.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我有個驚喜要送給他們\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But I have a surprise for them.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.18,0:05:31.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（W 壓縮氧）
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.61,0:05:36.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傳下去\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Heave.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.15,0:05:40.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點傳\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Heave.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.45,0:05:44.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管這些錫罐是做什么用的 肯定不是什么好事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Well, whatever these tin cans are for can't be good.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.74,0:05:46.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,派克 你有什么計劃\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Pike, man, what's the plan?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.16,0:05:51.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,專心干活\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Keep your eyes on your work.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.41,0:05:53.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-繼續傳 -嘿 別呆站著\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Heave. - And quit standing around! Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.29,0:05:57.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點 你在干什么呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Come on. What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.25,0:06:00.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 該行動了 我去引開他們 你們去找魯絲\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- All right, time to move. I'll distract them. You guys get to Ruth.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.13,0:06:03.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 不能這么做\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- No. Whoa, whoa. That's not how it works, man.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.84,0:06:05.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你現在是負責人了 你不能被抓\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You're in charge now. You don't get caught.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.27,0:06:14.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接著\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Catch.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.04,0:06:37.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們已經就位\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- We're in position.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.46,0:06:39.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（冷封門已鎖）
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.63,0:06:40.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（冷封門解鎖）
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.80,0:06:42.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喬西 是時候了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Josie, it's time.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.51,0:06:44.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在外面當心點\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Be careful out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.38,0:06:47.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會毀掉那引擎的 別擔心\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- I'll breach the bastard, don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.02,0:06:54.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是現在 魚叉炮\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Now! Harpoon!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.27,0:06:55.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,準備發射\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Deploy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.40,0:07:01.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正在打開冷封門\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Opening cold-lock.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.75,0:07:14.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,威爾福德有一個 像大炮的玩意兒 往后撤\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Wilford has a cannon or something. Pull back!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.83,0:07:16.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬上更換軌道 喬西 抓緊了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Switch track. Josie, hold on.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.71,0:07:19.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（軌道切換）
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.64,0:07:30.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-我們要脫軌了 -設法穩住\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- We're derailing! - Try to stabilize.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.06,0:07:33.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干得漂亮\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Well done.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.73,0:07:38.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你總能令我驚訝\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Never fails to amaze me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.44,0:07:41.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,受到這么大刺激 卻沒什么反應\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You take so much in and give so little back.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.61,0:07:45.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我剛射殘了你男人的列車 扎拉 可你連眼睛都沒眨一下\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I just hobbled your man, Zarah, and you didn't even flinch.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.87,0:07:52.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,照這個速度下去 黎明前這場戰爭就會結束\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}At this rate, the war will be over by daybreak.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.38,0:08:08.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托 嘿 這節車廂受損 我們得離開這里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Come on. The car is damaged. We gotta go. Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.80,0:08:12.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得把車廂斷開 否則我們會脫軌的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- We have to cut it loose. It's gonna derail us.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.39,0:08:13.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從這里斷開 那可是四節車廂啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Cut here? That's four cars.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.93,0:08:16.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是最近的連接處 這是唯一的選擇\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- It's the closest J-link. It's the only option.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.31,0:08:18.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-阿莎在那后面 -我們沒時間了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Asha's back there. - We don't have time.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.73,0:08:20.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快走\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Go.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.06,0:08:22.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你沒事吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- You okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.15,0:08:22.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.07,0:08:26.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她在外頭堅持了八年 不能上我們列車第二天就被害死呀\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- She waited eight years outside. Can't very well kill her on day two.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.94,0:08:27.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安全栓已解除\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Safety's off.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.12,0:08:33.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開始斷開連接\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Disconnecting now
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.29,0:08:35.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（連接處解鎖）
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.54,0:08:37.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,斷開了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And we're clear.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.55,0:08:47.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這邊走\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.60,0:08:54.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在這里會更安全\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You'll be safer up here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.85,0:08:58.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.85,0:09:02.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不會有事吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You gonna be okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.94,0:09:07.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把燈關了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Turn out the lights.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.07,0:09:10.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒問題\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.24,0:09:15.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,待著別動 好嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hold fast, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.29,0:09:59.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們有麻煩了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- We have a problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.45,0:10:01.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,威爾福德不見了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Wilford's gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.29,0:10:05.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他關閉了列車的信號和燈光 不知道他們在哪里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}His train went dark. He could be anywhere now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.42,0:10:14.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,關閉全車上下的通訊和信號傳輸 停止一切聲響\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Switch off comms and transmitters tip to tail. Not a peep.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.85,0:10:22.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,扎拉 你怎么還站著呀\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Zarah, what are you doing still on your feet?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.73,0:10:24.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你一定累壞了 過來\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You must be exhausted. Come.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.40,0:10:29.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你有什么打算\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- So what are you planning?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.82,0:10:34.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍微歇一下對我們有好處\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Bit of a lull. It'll do us good.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.03,0:10:40.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喘口氣\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Catch our breath.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.62,0:10:44.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在你和這孩子身上投入了很多\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I've invested a lot in you. And the child.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.92,0:10:48.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是想讓你待在我身邊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I just want to keep you near me,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.21,0:10:49.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了保護你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}for your protection.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.38,0:10:53.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且如果我在機車里 他們就不會攻擊這里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- And because they won't attack the engine if I'm in it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.97,0:10:54.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.65,0:11:12.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,十幾公里長的列車 你怎么能跟丟了呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- How do you lose a 10-mile train?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.74,0:11:15.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我們把他帶到這片迷宮里的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- We were the ones that led him into this maze.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.24,0:11:17.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他可能想逃出去 這六條線路通向谷外\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- He could be running. These six routes head out of the valley.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.82,0:11:19.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果他進入了直線軌道 我們就失去了優勢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}If he gets to linear track, we'll lose our advantage.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.87,0:11:22.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 他也可能 正在下一個拐角等著我們\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Yeah, or he's around the next corner, laying in wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.45,0:11:24.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他會把我們的列車一節節地廢掉\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- He's gonna pick us off piece by piece.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.71,0:11:26.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當時那玩意的炮口正對著我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I looked into the muzzle of that thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.37,0:11:28.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們必須找到他 我們能去高一點的地方嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- We need to get eyes on him. Can we get to higher ground?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.96,0:11:32.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這里 這條軌道沿著山脊線 應該能讓我們看到整個盆地\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Here, track follows the ridgeline. Should give us a view of the whole basin.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.42,0:11:35.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 就這么辦 把燈熄了 如果他打算隱身 我們也一樣\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Okay, let's do it. Lights out. If he's gonna go dark, so do we.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.48,0:11:48.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小情侶 起來干活了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Up and at 'em, lovebirds.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.23,0:11:51.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凱文 出去 你太過分了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Kevin! Get out. How dare you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.65,0:11:53.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夜車被我征用了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Commandeering the Nightcar.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.23,0:11:54.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凱文\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Ugh, Kevin.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.40,0:11:55.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰批準的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- On whose authority?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.57,0:11:58.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你可以稱之為“戰時舉措”\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Call it a wartime measure.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.11,0:12:01.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們沒聽說嗎 雷頓回來了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Oh, you didn't hear? Layton's back.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.91,0:12:02.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,起來\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Up.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.49,0:12:04.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有活兒要干呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}There's work to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.89,0:12:27.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要不你去煮點咖啡吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Why don't you, um, go put some coffee on?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.91,0:12:41.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰在那里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Who--who's there?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.70,0:12:45.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是來見囚犯的 我是她的律師\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Here to see the prisoner. I'm her lawyer.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.33,0:12:47.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得現在已經沒有律師這回事了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- I don't think that's a thing anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.21,0:12:50.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,軍靴 你把頭盔摘掉了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Lose your helmet, Jackboot?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.33,0:12:51.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿 別這樣 哥們\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Hey, come on, man.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.00,0:12:52.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.50,0:12:54.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你認識我嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Do you know me?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.71,0:12:59.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是個末等人 抱歉 我不知道你叫什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- You're--you're a Tailie. Forgive me, I-I don't know your name.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.43,0:13:01.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我認識你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- I know you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.72,0:13:03.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你姓惠金斯\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Whiggins.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.51,0:13:05.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.97,0:13:08.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,關于末等人 有兩件事你該知道\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Well, there's two things you should know about Tailies.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.23,0:13:12.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們的記性很好 而且打仗我們總贏\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We have long memories and we win wars.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.81,0:13:13.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Oh, yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.32,0:13:18.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上一場戰爭是我們贏了 這一場也一樣\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We won the last one. And we'll win this one.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.74,0:13:22.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想當個礙我們事的人嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And do you wanna be the guy who stands in the way?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.37,0:13:24.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,惠金斯\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hmm, Whiggins?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.49,0:13:29.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,律師先生 給你十分鐘的時間\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- You have ten minutes, Counselor.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.00,0:13:32.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我替你開門\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Let me just get the door for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.47,0:13:41.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,派克\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Pike?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.38,0:13:43.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姑娘 你的氣色不錯啊 沒有缺胳膊少腿\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- You're looking good, girl, with those arms dangling down.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.84,0:13:46.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不該來這里 太危險了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- You shouldn't be here. It's too dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.64,0:13:49.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-我得把你弄出去 -等等 告訴我發生了什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- I'm gonna get you out of here. - Wait, wait, wait. Tell me what happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.35,0:13:53.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,威爾福德用大炮把雷頓趕走了 此刻我們正在黑暗中瞎轉\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Wilford drove Layton off with cannon fire. Now we're rolling around in the dark.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.19,0:13:58.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果威爾福德在躲著雷頓 那我們就得給雷頓發信號\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Well, if Wilford is hiding, then we need to signal Layton.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.57,0:14:00.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我得先把你救出去\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- I'm gonna get you out of here first.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.69,0:14:04.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行的 要救我 你得先殺了惠金斯 然后找到克利福德\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- You can't. You'd have to kill Whiggins, and then you'd have to find Clifford
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.57,0:14:06.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把他也殺了 因為鑰匙在他手里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and kill him too, 'cause he's got the keys.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.08,0:14:08.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有誰 繼續說\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Go on.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.20,0:14:11.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,派克先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Pike, Mr. Pike,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.16,0:14:14.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是個好人 一個勇敢的好人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}you're a dear man and a brave one,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.29,0:14:17.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但這場戰爭比你我都重要\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}but this war is bigger than us.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.76,0:14:22.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要怎么給雷頓發信號呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- How do I signal Layton?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.39,0:14:26.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有個主意\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- I've got an idea,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.01,0:14:29.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但你得去列車前列的待客部\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}but you'll have to get uptrain to hospitality.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.23,0:14:42.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿莎 你還好嗎 在這里還行嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Asha. Hey, you good in there?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.61,0:14:47.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 我們讓你卷進了 最激烈的對抗中 來\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm sorry, I dropped you right in the thick of it. Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.20,0:14:48.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hey, hey, hey, hey, hey, hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.03,0:14:50.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發生什么事了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.54,0:14:52.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,威爾福德先生把這列車弄壞了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Did Mr. Wilford cripple the train?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.66,0:14:55.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有 聽著 這只是貓鼠之爭 好嗎 沒事的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- No, look, it's just some cat and mouse, all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.21,0:14:56.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們是貓\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.88,0:14:58.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們八個人 要對付偉大的威爾福德先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- And you're supposed to be the cat? Eight of you against the great Mr. Wilford.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.79,0:15:01.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“偉大的威爾福德先生” 跟你想象中的不一樣\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- The great Mr. Wilford is not who you think he is.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.13,0:15:02.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是他救了你們大家嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Isn't he the one that saved all of you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.92,0:15:04.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我們自己救了自己\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- We saved our own damn selves.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.51,0:15:06.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他打造這列列車 只是為了自己能稱王\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He built all of this just so he could be king.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.80,0:15:09.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-那現在輪到你稱王了 -不 這是我們的私人恩怨 好嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- So now it's your turn? - No. This is personal for us, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.06,0:15:12.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,登上列車時 我有一個伴侶 她現在懷著身孕\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I have a partner that I boarded with. I have a child on the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.85,0:15:19.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你這么做是為了一個孩子 你會做出讓自己后悔的事的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Oh, if you're doing this for a child, you will do things that you will regret.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.36,0:15:22.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是過來警告你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- I just came in to warn you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.40,0:15:24.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們不會放棄的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We are not giving up.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.15,0:15:27.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,局勢好轉之前 會變得更加惡劣 明白嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This is gonna get worse before it gets better, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.99,0:15:29.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-明白 -堅持住\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Okay. - Hold on.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.88,0:15:43.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是我的陽光\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- ♪ You are my sunshine
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.71,0:15:47.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我唯一的陽光\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}♪ My only sunshine
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.68,0:15:51.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當天空灰暗時\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}♪ You make me happy
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.10,0:15:54.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會帶給我歡樂\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}♪ When skies are gray
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.77,0:15:58.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你永遠都不知\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}♪ You'll never know, dear
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.65,0:16:02.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有多么愛你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}♪ How much I love you
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.86,0:16:09.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請別將我的陽光帶走\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}♪ Please don't take My sunshine away
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.53,0:16:11.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要知道 你唱歌的時候\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- You know, when you sing,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.70,0:16:15.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我幾乎都能說服自己說 你的為人并不壞\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I can almost convince myself you're not a horrible person.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.37,0:16:17.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.00,0:16:22.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后我會想起來你只翻唱別人的歌 所以歌詞其實不代表你的心聲\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- And then I remember you only sing covers, so the words aren't actually yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.88,0:16:24.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歌詞只是點綴而已\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Lyrics are just dressing.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.51,0:16:26.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只為他歌唱\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I sing for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.63,0:16:28.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老天\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Oh, God.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.84,0:16:30.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你顯得很不屑\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- You scoff,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.89,0:16:34.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但歸根結底 那就是全部\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}but at the end of the day, that's all there is.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.02,0:16:36.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你為之歌唱的那個人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}A person you sing for.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.78,0:16:46.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貝絲 你的那個人是誰\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Who's that to you, Bess?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.91,0:16:57.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你一路堅持到了世界末日 居然會沒有一個那樣的人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}How do you get all the way to the end of the world and have no one?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.54,0:16:59.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- I have people.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.54,0:17:02.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Who?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.59,0:17:06.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷頓、扎拉、羅齊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Layton, Zarah, Roche.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.84,0:17:08.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,羅齊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Roche?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.76,0:17:10.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯 羅齊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Yeah, Roche.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.18,0:17:13.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他就像我的導師兼益友\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He was like a mentor to me and--and a friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.22,0:17:18.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,盡管我跟他對著干 他還是罩著我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Even though I fought him, he-- he had my back.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.69,0:17:22.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 我不會為他歌唱\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No, I don't-- I don't sing for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.86,0:17:24.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是每一天\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But not a day goes
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.94,0:17:27.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都在想著把他從抽屜房弄出來\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}by when I don't think about getting him out of those Drawers.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.07,0:17:31.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很遺憾\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.99,0:17:35.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望他能活下來\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I hope he survived.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.54,0:17:38.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是呀\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.67,0:17:48.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們在山脊上了 注意觀察\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- We're at the ridge. Eyes up.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.13,0:17:51.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果他在山谷里 這是能找到他的最佳位置\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}If he is in the valley, this is the best vantage point.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.27,0:18:01.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-有發現嗎  -提爾\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Anything? - Till?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.52,0:18:02.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有 什么都沒發現\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Negative. There's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.19,0:18:05.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但他們不可能就這樣消失不見啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- But they can't just vanish.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.78,0:18:12.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（待客部）
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.22,0:18:39.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（W 新年流程）
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.31,0:18:40.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好戲登場\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Time to put on a show.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.34,0:19:11.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看南面 在山谷的盡頭 你們看到了嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}To the south, far end of the valley. Are you guys seeing this?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.63,0:19:14.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的天啊 等等\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Oh, my God. Wait, wait, wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.76,0:19:15.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Is that-
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.43,0:19:18.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們的支持者還在\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They're still with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.85,0:19:29.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看到你了 約瑟夫\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- We see you, Joseph.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.88,0:19:53.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他正試圖逃跑 在山脊東側 往干線方向去\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- He's making a break for it. East over the ridge to the trunk line.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.96,0:19:57.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他想偷偷溜出鐵路站場 我們在這里有戰術優勢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He wants to sneak out of the rail yard because it's where we have tactical advantage.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.51,0:20:00.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他要是跑出去了 接下去好幾天就都是直線軌道\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- If he gets out of the valley, he's looking at days of linear track.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.10,0:20:01.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們能趕到他前面去嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Can we beat him to it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.72,0:20:03.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-艾莉  -不行\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Alex? - No.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.18,0:20:06.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道 也許行吧 我沒把握\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I don't know, maybe. It's all assumptions.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.27,0:20:07.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我們還等什么 加速啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- What are we waiting for? Pedal down.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.98,0:20:09.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們在山口截住他\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Let's cut 'em off at the pass.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.98,0:20:13.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,工程師 加足馬力\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Full throttle, Engineer.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.48,0:20:15.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先生 恕我直言 我們的油耗非常快\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Sir, with respect, we're draining really fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.74,0:20:17.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍微開慢點 燃油效率會更高\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}A few ticks slower would be more efficient.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.57,0:20:19.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們已經看到我們了 他們要來了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- They've seen us. They're coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.99,0:20:24.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用上所有的儲備燃油 越過這該死的山脊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Tap every last reserve and get us over that bloody ridge!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.80,0:20:37.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托 你這是干什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Come on! What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.18,0:20:42.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,強壯男孩 給你挑\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- So you have a choice, Strong Boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.55,0:20:47.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來要我砸碎兩根手指呢 還是砸碎你的拇指\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I can take two fingers next time or I can take your thumb.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.77,0:20:49.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也可以聰明一點\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Or you could be smart
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.81,0:20:52.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像你自告奮勇 到我桌子這里來時一樣\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}like when you bravely volunteered to step up to my table here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.57,0:20:57.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,威爾福德只是要你提供信息 報出你同黨的姓名\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Wilford just needs you to start talking and name your collaborators.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.03,0:21:00.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不干\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.91,0:21:05.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-不干  -拜托 別再折磨他了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- No? - Come on. Leave him alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.54,0:21:10.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-抓住他 -不要\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Hold him. - Ah, no! No!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.55,0:21:17.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夠了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.84,0:21:23.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒答應過要趟這渾水\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- I didn't sign up for this.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.51,0:21:25.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是想經營夜總會 提供酒水和歌曲\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Just wanted to serve some drinks and play some tunes.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.60,0:21:28.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你能放松點嗎 戰爭都是丑陋的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Would you relax? War is not pretty.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.89,0:21:30.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但威爾福德會獎勵我們的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But Wilford will reward us.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.44,0:21:32.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前提是他能贏\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- If he wins.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.48,0:21:34.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他當然會贏\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Of course he'll win.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.98,0:21:37.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萬一他輸了呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}If he doesn't?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.36,0:21:39.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到時候雷頓進來發現這件事 知道我們也在場 怎么辦\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- And Layton rolls in here, finds this? Finds us?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.24,0:21:42.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,威爾福德的傀儡夫妻\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Wilford's little wedding puppets.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.99,0:21:46.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行刑的人又不是我們 我們只是提供了場地而已\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- We're not the torturers, all right? We're just providing a venue.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.62,0:21:49.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得被肢解的這個家伙 可不會這么認為\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- I'm sure the mutilated guy will be quick to sort that out.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.50,0:21:53.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽著 如果你不打算開口\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Look, if you're not gonna talk,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.63,0:21:56.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你就不再需要這舌頭了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I guess you don't need that tongue anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.46,0:21:57.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請抓好他\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hold him, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.51,0:22:04.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抓好他\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hold him, hold him.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.51,0:22:06.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,張嘴\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Open up.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.78,0:22:27.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽著 即便我們追上了他 我們還是要應付他的魚叉炮\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Look, even if we catch up with him, we still have the harpoon issue,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.66,0:22:29.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們也沒法進行車尾對接\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and we can't connect end to end.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.12,0:22:31.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我們絕對打不過他的軍靴\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We'll never overpower his Jackboots.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.87,0:22:33.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- No.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.17,0:22:34.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- No.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.42,0:22:39.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我們得想辦法進入機車 我們需要引開他的注意力\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So we need a plan to get into his engine. We need a distraction.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.92,0:22:42.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奧德麗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Audrey.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.14,0:22:54.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是要干什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.15,0:22:56.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手放在背后\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Hands behind your back.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.52,0:22:59.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手銬 我就知道你有性怪癖\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Ooh, handcuffs. I knew you had a kink.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.61,0:23:02.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快走\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Move.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.24,0:23:06.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祝好運\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Good luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.66,0:23:15.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這里的氣氛很壓抑嘛\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- It's moody in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.00,0:23:17.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坐下\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Sit.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.51,0:23:23.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有多遠\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- How much further?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.51,0:23:28.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快到山脊了 但我們的燃油即將耗盡\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- We're almost at the ridge, but we're basically running on fumes.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.22,0:23:31.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,繼續開 它能行的 然后就勝券在握了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Keep pushing. She'll make it. Then we're home free.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.52,0:23:36.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悠著點 本\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Nice and easy, Ben.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.70,0:23:49.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,約瑟夫\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Joseph.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.92,0:24:08.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大愛麗絲 這里是雪國列車 請回話\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Big Alice, this is Snowpiercer. Come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.26,0:24:14.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪國列車呼叫大愛麗絲 請回話\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Snowpiercer to Big Alice, come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.18,0:24:15.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先生 我該回答嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Sir, should--should I answer?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.35,0:24:16.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- No, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.98,0:24:22.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大愛麗絲 請回答\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Come in, Big Alice.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.32,0:24:30.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這里是大愛麗絲 我在跟誰通話呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- This is Big Alice. To whom am I speaking?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.49,0:24:34.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,威爾福德 我是那個 擋在你和開放軌道之間的人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- I'm the guy standing between you and open track, Wilford.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.29,0:24:39.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看到了 這么說 現在就看誰的膽子更大了 是嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- I see that. So it's a game of chicken, is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.79,0:24:42.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,按你們行進的速度 我覺得你開不到那么遠\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- At the rate you're going, I don't think you'll make it this far.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.75,0:24:46.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大愛麗絲的韌勁比你想象的強\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Oh, Big Alice has more fight than you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.13,0:24:48.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷頓 這次會面是你發起的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You called this meeting, Layton.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.72,0:24:55.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 有話快說 沒必要在這里做無聊的爭執\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So go on, or are we just gonna stand here pissing off our prows?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.64,0:24:58.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們離開時 你我有個約定\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- When we left, we made a deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:59.52,0:25:00.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我確保奧德麗安全…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I keep Audrey safe--
Dialogue: 0,0:25:00.98,0:25:03.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我記得 我就不把大家殺了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- I remember, and I don't murder everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:03.36,0:25:04.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 我記得我們的約定\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yes, I remember the deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:04.86,0:25:08.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要提醒你一句 那是在脅迫下作出的約定\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It was made under duress, I'll remind you.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:08.24,0:25:09.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我還是遵守了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But I stuck to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:10.16,0:25:11.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,扎拉呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Where's Zarah?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:14.28,0:25:15.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她就在這里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- She's right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:17.37,0:25:18.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,滿面紅光\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Positively glowing.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:18.79,0:25:20.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在這里 安德烈 我沒事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- I'm here, Andre. I'm okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:22.13,0:25:22.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奧德麗呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- And Audrey?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:24.54,0:25:25.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想聽到她的聲音\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I want to hear her.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:29.84,0:25:31.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我得知道她沒事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I need to know she's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:34.55,0:25:37.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交出列車控制權 你就可以親自跟她說話了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Surrender the train and you can tell her yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:40.23,0:25:41.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交出控制權\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Surrender?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:41.19,0:25:44.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們會給你們一節頭等車廂 提供美食酒水\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- We'll give you a car in First, food, drink.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:45.44,0:25:47.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們倆可以相守到老\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You two can live out your years together.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:48.53,0:25:52.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說 我把一切都給你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- So I--I give you absolutely everything,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:53.37,0:25:55.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而你只會給我一點小小的恩賜\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and you give me a little piece back in return?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:55.87,0:25:57.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個提議太可笑了吧 雷頓\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That's quite some offer, Layton.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:57.83,0:26:01.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的提議是 用非暴力的形式了結這件事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- The offer is, we end this without violence,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:01.79,0:26:07.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,否則就回到那個鐵路站場 我們會把你拆成碎片\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}or you could roll back down into that rail yard and we'll pick you apart.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:07.17,0:26:08.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完了 先生 燃油耗盡了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- That's it, sir. We're tapped.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:12.68,0:26:13.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我拒絕\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- No deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:32.61,0:26:36.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想聽聽她的聲音\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I...I want to hear her voice.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:51.09,0:26:51.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,約瑟夫\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Joseph.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:10.86,0:27:12.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（危險）
Dialogue: 0,0:27:14.28,0:27:15.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 本 我到冷封門了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- All right, Ben, I'm at the cold-Lock.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:27.71,0:27:30.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Soon, soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:42.14,0:27:43.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,設置自動駕駛 急速后退\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Auto-engaging hot reverse.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:43.81,0:27:46.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們應該調換一下車尾車頭 讓大愛麗絲在后面推\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We should switch helms and get Big Alice pushing again.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:47.19,0:27:48.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,停車 工程師\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Full stop, Engineer.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:50.44,0:27:52.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,關閉電源\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Let her power down.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:52.28,0:27:53.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-什么  -約瑟夫\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- What? - Joseph.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:01.12,0:28:02.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這不可能是好事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- That can't be good,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:03.04,0:28:03.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會是好事嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}can it?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:04.66,0:28:05.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- No.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:07.00,0:28:08.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪國列車\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Snowpiercer,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:09.08,0:28:10.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們沒動力 啟動不了了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}we are dead on the tracks.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:10.92,0:28:14.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你們不跟我們連接 列車上所有的人都會凍死\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}If you don't reconnect, everyone will freeze to death.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:21.97,0:28:23.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這是不顧一切了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- You're desperate.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:24.56,0:28:26.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而你則沒得選擇\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- And you have no choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:31.36,0:28:34.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,準備連接 哈維…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Prepare to connect. Javi, abre una cerveza, amigo.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:40.03,0:28:43.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,指揮官 把你的突擊小組 派到連接點去\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Commander, move your boarding party to the connection point.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:46.12,0:28:47.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發電不足容量\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Generation deficit.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:47.12,0:28:49.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,整個列車的溫度正在下降\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Train-wide temperature is dropping right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:49.92,0:28:51.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最好把你的毛衣穿上\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Better get your woolies on.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:52.13,0:28:53.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來吧 小伙子們 準備好了嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- All right, boys, you ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:55.71,0:28:59.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出去 瞄準中心點 記住射擊目標\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Move out. Remember where to aim.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:59.84,0:29:01.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們在準備連接了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- They're preparing to dock.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:02.85,0:29:04.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們別無選擇\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- They've got no choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:04.14,0:29:07.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又要開始了 快走 快\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Let's go, let's go. Move, move, move.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:07.77,0:29:09.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,駕駛艙沒問題\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Cap okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:12.44,0:29:14.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿 留神點 進去\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Hey, watch your back. Move it, move it!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:17.53,0:29:18.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這太瘋狂了 本\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- This is crazy, Ben.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:19.07,0:29:20.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是呀 強盜生涯就是如此\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Yeah, pirate's life.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:20.99,0:29:22.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,見鬼\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Shit.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:22.37,0:29:23.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- You're all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:23.49,0:29:25.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用你敢開的最快速度倒車\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Just reverse her in as fast as you dare.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:26.08,0:29:27.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,見鬼\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Shit.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:29.04,0:29:31.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們就位之前不要與對方連接\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- And don't reconnect until we're in position.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:38.80,0:29:41.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 各位 記住 我們要先把對方清除干凈\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Hey, remember, people, we're gonna clear it first.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:41.55,0:29:44.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,武器準備好 上\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Weapons ready? Move!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:54.31,0:29:55.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老天\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Christ.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:56.27,0:29:57.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喬瑟芬\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Josephine.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:58.65,0:29:59.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她回來了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}She's back.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:00.86,0:30:03.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真夠有種的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The bloody balls.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:06.58,0:30:08.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是爬上來的嗎 小流浪漢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Did you climb aboard, you little hobo?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:11.58,0:30:13.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這里有孕婦哦\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Uh-uh, baby on board.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:14.42,0:30:17.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 你不會的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No, you won't.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:17.71,0:30:18.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她不會的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}She won't.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:24.30,0:30:27.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,見鬼 真夠狠的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Damn. Good one.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:58.84,0:31:03.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫你的人退下 否則我就把你扔出列車去\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Tell your men to stand down or I will throw you off this train.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:17.06,0:31:18.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是首席工程師威爾福德\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- This is Head Engineer Wilford.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:20.61,0:31:22.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突擊小組 退下\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Boarding party, stand down.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:28.03,0:31:29.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們不打算…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We will not be taking...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:32.20,0:31:33.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用武力拿下雪國列車\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Snowpiercer by force.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:38.58,0:31:40.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,退下 放下武器\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Stand down. Weapons down.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:42.21,0:31:43.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的天啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Oh, my God.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:54.64,0:31:55.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這下開心了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Happy now?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:57.65,0:31:58.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快說\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Say it!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:10.24,0:32:14.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安德烈雷頓擁有了列車控制權\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Andre Layton has the train.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:18.29,0:32:19.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪國列車的公民們…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Citizens of Snowpiercer...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:27.34,0:32:28.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們回來了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We're back.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:54.49,0:32:57.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,50米 40米\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}50 meters, 40 meters,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:58.04,0:32:59.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,25米\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}25 meters...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:10.80,0:33:12.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能就這樣結束了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- It can't be just over.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:16.97,0:33:20.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得該是選擇勝利一方的時候了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Well, I think it's about time we get on the right side of history.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:32.57,0:33:33.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Here you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:41.17,0:33:42.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奧斯\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Oz,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:43.63,0:33:44.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我非常愛你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I love you so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:05.82,0:34:07.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抵抗軍萬歲\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Long live the Resistance!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:56.16,0:34:57.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-找到了 -魯絲\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Ah, found it. - Ruth?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:59.95,0:35:01.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安德烈\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Andre.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:02.91,0:35:04.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你沒穿制服 我都認不出你了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- I never would have found you. You're in civvies.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:07.79,0:35:10.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我記得威爾福德 把他的好酒藏在這里了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I remembered that Wilford had a secret tipple up here.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:11.38,0:35:14.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-我正需要喝兩口 沒錯 -我想著我們可以慶祝一下\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Oh, could use some of that. - Wanna celebrate? - Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:14.88,0:35:17.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎回來 你能回來真是太好了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Oh, welcome home. It's good to have you back.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:21.02,0:35:22.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就知道你能把大家團結在一起\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- I knew you'd hold everyone together.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:23.02,0:35:23.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干得漂亮\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well done.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:27.27,0:35:28.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們來喝吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Let's do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:28.73,0:35:29.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把他們放出來\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Take them out.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:34.95,0:35:36.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他情況穩定\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- He's stable.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:41.95,0:35:44.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡莉情況穩定…還有安娜…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Carly's stable. And Anne--
Dialogue: 0,0:36:39.51,0:36:40.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈維\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Javi.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:52.82,0:36:53.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:02.66,0:37:03.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Oh, man.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:11.83,0:37:16.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非洲之角這個暖點 你真的相信它能維持生命生長\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- This warm spot, the Horn of Africa, you really believe it can support life?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:16.63,0:37:20.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 魯絲 我們的未來就在那里 我非常堅信這一點\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Yeah, our future is there, Ruth. I believe it with all my heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:22.26,0:37:25.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通往非洲之角的軌道是整個鐵路網內\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- You know, the Horn of Africa, the approach is maybe the worst stretch of track on
Dialogue: 0,0:37:25.31,0:37:26.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最糟的一段\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}the entire network.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:26.43,0:37:28.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且氣候崩潰時 那里發生過一場戰爭\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And there was a war there when the climate crashed.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:28.56,0:37:29.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 我記得\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Yeah, yeah, I remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:31.19,0:37:32.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都累壞了 安德烈\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- The people are tired, Andre.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:32.48,0:37:34.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這六個月艱苦漫長 而你回來后的第一個命令\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's been a long six months, and your first order
Dialogue: 0,0:37:34.61,0:37:36.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是要讓他們再經歷更多艱辛\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}is gonna be to steer them right back into more hardship?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:36.73,0:37:38.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不會下達命令 我們會投票決定\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Mm-mmm, there won't be an order. We'll put it to a vote.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:40.70,0:37:42.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-投票  -是的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- A vote? - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:42.16,0:37:45.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們要讓大家看看 民主已經獲勝 我們要一起選擇前進的道路\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We'll show them that democracy has won. We'll choose our path forward together.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:47.20,0:37:49.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你已經準備好面對投票結果了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- And you're prepared for the outcome of this vote?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:49.79,0:37:52.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會讓大家相信這值得冒險一試\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- I am going to convince them that it is worth the risk.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:53.00,0:37:55.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪國列車已經損毀不堪 不拋錨已是萬幸\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Snowpiercer's running on duct tape and prayers.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:55.21,0:37:57.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是一個真實的能下車的機會\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This is a real opportunity to get off.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:59.76,0:38:01.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這也是對你的投票 安德烈\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- It's also a vote on you, Andre.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:02.43,0:38:04.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,列車上的很多人并不支持你的領導\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Much of the train doesn't support your leadership.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:05.89,0:38:07.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這件事不止關系到我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- This isn't just about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:08.60,0:38:10.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這也是梅蘭妮會想要的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's what Melanie would have wanted.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:11.98,0:38:12.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:13.31,0:38:15.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去通知公證處\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'll, uh, inform the notary.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:16.23,0:38:18.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道列車上的所有人 都會慎重地投出這一票\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I know that everyone aboard will take their vote to heart,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:19.40,0:38:21.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但萬一投票結果是“不去” 你有這思想準備嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}but are you prepared to accept it if they vote no?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:24.66,0:38:27.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你最好仔細琢磨一下要怎么說服大家\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You better think long and hard about exactly what it is you're gonna tell them.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:36.96,0:38:40.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只準你待在三等車廂 而且禁止進夜車\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- You're confined to Third and barred from the Nightcar.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:40.17,0:38:42.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-約瑟夫呢  -奧德麗 你站錯隊伍了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Where's Joseph? - You picked the wrong side, Audrey.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:46.30,0:38:49.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這該死的列車上有過正確的隊伍嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Has there ever been a right side on this goddamn train?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:51.27,0:38:53.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這一切都會崩塌的 等著瞧吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's all gonna go to shit. You'll see.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:07.70,0:39:09.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直接扎穿了我的手\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- It went straight through my hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:10.91,0:39:12.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣你就能記住我們了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Something to remember us by.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:14.04,0:39:15.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看看你呀\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Look at you.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:15.96,0:39:18.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怪物來找它的創造者\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}A monster come for its creator.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:20.67,0:39:22.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很有詩意吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's poetic, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:25.63,0:39:27.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷頓沒法把列車團結起來的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Layton can't hold it together, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:29.18,0:39:30.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們會再次拒絕他的領導\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They'll reject him again.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:33.18,0:39:34.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是這列車的靈魂\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I am the train.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:48.53,0:39:49.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,投票\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- A vote?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:50.83,0:39:51.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:53.79,0:39:55.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你今天也會有投票的權利\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You'll get a vote today too.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:58.33,0:39:59.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,政治\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Politics.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:00.00,0:40:02.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當你是世上最后一個人的時候 就會忘記政治的存在\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You forget about them when you're the last person on Earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:05.26,0:40:06.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:07.01,0:40:08.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先別忙著謝我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Don't thank me just yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:09.14,0:40:10.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有件事要你幫忙\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}There's something I need to ask of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:12.81,0:40:14.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安德烈 你救了我的命\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- You brought me back to life, Andre.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:18.02,0:40:19.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要我幫什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:01.98,0:41:03.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位乘客同伴們\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- My fellow passengers...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:06.15,0:41:10.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天是這列列車啟程以來第一次\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Today, for the first time since our departure...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:12.78,0:41:15.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由你們來決定我們的目的地\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}you will have a say in our destination,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:16.83,0:41:18.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且你們的選擇將決定我們的未來\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and your choice will determine our future.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:19.00,0:41:23.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們已經知道 梅蘭妮犧牲了自己 為我們繪制了一份地圖\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}By now, you know that Melanie's sacrifice gave us a map.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:24.04,0:41:27.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,證明地球上有些地方正在變暖\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Proof that there are places on the Earth that are warming.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:28.55,0:41:31.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們之前輕裝出發 快速地測試了每一個暖點\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Traveling fast and light, we tested each of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:32.55,0:41:36.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蘇拉威西島、古吉拉特邦、馬那瓜\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Sulawesi, Gujarat, Managua,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:37.85,0:41:39.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿塔卡馬\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}the Atacama.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:40.31,0:41:42.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但它們都不合格\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And each one of these let us down.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:43.23,0:41:46.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道 當初我們分開列車的決定\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I know that you have suffered badly
Dialogue: 0,0:41:47.40,0:41:49.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,害你們歷盡了艱苦\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}because of our decision to break the train.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:50.74,0:41:54.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但還有一個地方 我覺得大家應該寄予希望\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But there is one more location on which I ask you to stake your hope:
Dialogue: 0,0:41:56.08,0:41:57.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是非洲之角\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}the Horn of Africa.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:58.87,0:42:01.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,返回那里的行程會充滿風險\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The journey to return there will be fraught with risk
Dialogue: 0,0:42:01.33,0:42:03.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艱辛還將繼續\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and the hardships will continue,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:03.88,0:42:07.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但這里有一個人 能讓我們重樹信心\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}but we have someone here who can renew our faith.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:11.47,0:42:13.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一個我們以前覺得不可能存在的人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Someone we had given up on believing in.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:22.39,0:42:23.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他這是在干什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- What's he doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:24.10,0:42:25.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會讓她自己跟你們說\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- But I'll let her tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:26.86,0:42:28.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他在編瞎話\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- He's bullshitting.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:41.00,0:42:42.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫阿莎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- My name is Asha.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:44.67,0:42:46.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是一個幸存者\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I am a survivor.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:47.34,0:42:49.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷頓在外面找到了我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Layton found me out there, outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:50.55,0:42:54.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在戶外 生長了樹木\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Along with trees,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:54.93,0:42:56.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,青草\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}green grass...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:58.10,0:42:59.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和生命的地方\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and life.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:02.89,0:43:04.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我來自新伊甸園\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I come from New Eden.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:26.13,0:43:29.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是要你們 在我和威爾福德之間做出選擇\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- I'm not asking you to choose between me and Wilford.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:32.05,0:43:35.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而是請你們在我們熟悉的列車\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I am asking you to choose between the train we know
Dialogue: 0,0:43:36.39,0:43:38.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和我們不熟悉的夢想之間做出選擇\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and the dream we don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:41.85,0:43:44.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常感謝大家作出的犧牲\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Thank you all so much for your sacrifices.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:50.77,0:43:53.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個故事需要一個英雄 所以我們就帶回了一個英雄\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The story needed a hero, and we brought one back.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:54.53,0:43:57.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鑒于那番表演\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Well, in the wake of that performance,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:57.20,0:43:58.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,投贊同票的人勝出\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}the yeas have it.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:59.16,0:44:00.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幾乎是2比1的比例\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Almost two to one.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:02.79,0:44:03.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多說一個謊又怎樣呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- What's one more lie?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:03.91,0:44:06.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,區別在于 這是我們說的最后一個謊話\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- The difference is, this is the last one
Dialogue: 0,0:44:06.71,0:44:07.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很懷疑\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}we will have to tell.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:08.54,0:44:10.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我開始覺得這列列車需要謊言\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Well, I doubt that. I've come to think this train demands a lie.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:12.21,0:44:17.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯 就像虛構的機車中的天才\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Yeah, like an imaginary genius in the engine.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:17.43,0:44:20.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或是梅蘭妮用完美的科學手段 來拯救我們\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Or Melanie saving us with perfect science.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:20.55,0:44:23.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或是為我們指路的幸存者\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Or a survivor to show us the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:24.48,0:44:25.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- So...
Dialogue: 0,0:44:26.94,0:44:28.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-我們繼續前進 -同意\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}we press on. - Agreed.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:29.31,0:44:31.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們還能怎樣\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- What else are we gonna do?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:32.61,0:44:33.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喬西\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Josie?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:35.07,0:44:36.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們最好是對的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Well, we better be right.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:44.62,0:44:48.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位乘客同伴們 我們偉大的征程將繼續\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Fellow passengers, our great endeavor continues.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:49.04,0:44:55.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們已表態 根據少數服從多數原則 我們將前往新伊甸園\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You have spoken, and by majority rule, we are heading for New Eden.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:24.49,0:45:29.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,字幕翻譯：黛拉

